txt.en: Neutral to the Citizens of Umbar Baharbêl
The citizens of Umbar Baharbêl are wary of outsiders, but they no longer consider you a threat to their livelihoods, and you are welcome in the City of the Corsairs—at least for the moment.
You must earn Neutral standing with the the Citizens of Umbar Baharbêl
The Citizens of Umbar Baharbêl have come to know your name, yet still consider you an outsider.
